      <title>雷纳称艾伯特应获准再次代表工党参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rayner-says-abbott-should-be-allowed-to-stand-again-for-labour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党副领袖安吉拉·雷纳 (Angela Rayner) 表示，资深国会议员黛安·阿博特 (Diane Abbott) 应该被允许参加 7 月 4 日的大选，这表明工党高层在对待这位左翼议员的方式上存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rayner-says-abbott-should-be-allowed-to-stand-again-for-labour</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:28:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克工资上涨或导致 IMF 付款延迟至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/mozambique-s-surging-wage-bill-may-delay-imf-payment-to-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份文件显示，由于莫桑比克公共工资支出不断膨胀，该国从国际货币基金组织获得的下一笔付款面临被推迟的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/mozambique-s-surging-wage-bill-may-delay-imf-payment-to-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:25:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
